Class PublisherConst

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ejbca.core.model.ca.publisher.PublisherConst
  • public class PublisherConst
extends Object
    Constants for Publishers. Constants for Type of publisher: Type is constructed as a mask since one publisher can be of several types.
